						<p>On a stone bearing two footprints in the court-yard of the Śiva temple on the hillock.</p>						

						<p>Circa 16th century.</p>						

						<p>It seems to register a gift by certain officers and representatives of different coMmunities. The epigraph is incomplete. </p>						

